body: This is a missing method not from Rhino common itself but IronPython. Do you have another software (like Dynamo) that installs a different version of IronPython on your machine? The suggested solution is to remove the other IronPython installation or to install the latest version of IronPython. Doesn't necessary have to do anything with Ladybug and Honeybee itself. Also see this: [http://www.grasshopper3d.com/forum/topics/hb-and-lb-on-rhino-6-gh-1...](http://www.grasshopper3d.com/forum/topics/hb-and-lb-on-rhino-6-gh-1?groupUrl=ladybug&x=1&groupId=2985220%3AGroup%3A658987&id=2985220%3ATopic%3A1608402&page=2#comments)
